    "/api/v1/agent/session/{session_id}/access": {
      "patch": {
        "tags": [
          "agent"
        ],
        "summary": "Update Session Access",
        "description": "Update access control settings for a session.\n\n**Only the session owner can modify access settings.**\n\nOptions:\n- `is_public`: Set to true to allow anyone to access\n- `whitelist`: Replace the entire whitelist with new user IDs\n- `blacklist`: Replace the entire blacklist with new user IDs\n- `add_to_whitelist`: Add user IDs to the whitelist\n- `remove_from_whitelist`: Remove user IDs from the whitelist\n- `add_to_blacklist`: Add user IDs to the blacklist\n- `remove_from_blacklist`: Remove user IDs from the blacklist\n\n**Access Priority** (highest to lowest):\n1. Blacklist (always denied)\n2. Owner (always allowed)\n3. Public flag (if true, allows all except blacklisted)\n4. Whitelist (explicitly allowed)\n5. Default: Denied\n\n**Examples**:\n\nMake session public:\n```json\n{\"is_public\": true}\n```\n\nShare with specific users:\n```json\n{\"add_to_whitelist\": [\"user-123\", \"user-456\"]}\n```\n\nBlock specific users (even if public):\n```json\n{\"add_to_blacklist\": [\"spam-user\"]}\n```",
        "operationId": "update_session_access_api_v1_agent_session__session_id__access_patch",
        "security": [
          {
            "APIKeyHeader": []
          },
          {
            "APIKeyHeader": []
          }
        ],
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "session_id",
            "in": "path",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "description": "The session ID to update",
              "title": "Session Id"
            },
            "description": "The session ID to update"
          },
          {
            "name": "authorization",
            "in": "header",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "anyOf": [
                {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                {
                  "type": "null"
                }
              ],
              "title": "Authorization"
            }
          }
        ],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/AccessUpdateRequest"
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Successful Response",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
